author: travelblossom52
title: Great park n fly
text:
Room was spacious and clean. Linens and pillows are nice. I enjoyed the old fashioned pink tiles in the bathroom.
The area we stayed in was quiet. Park and fly was a good value for us. Stayed a night going and coming. Gone a month. Our car was parked in front of our room upon our return. Driver of the shuttle had our room and car keys. We'll stay here again when we fly.
